examples.en: The book is both scary and funny.
examples.ru: Книга одновременно и страшная, и смешная.

examples.en: Mommy, I had a really scary nightmare.

examples.en: It was scary being all alone in a strange city.

examples.en: The little girl was spooked by scary masks.

examples.en: The very thought of having to go through that again is scary

examples.en: The very thought of having to go through that again is scary.

examples.en: A first menstruation can be somewhat scary for girls who are unprepared.

examples.en: THey spent their nights around the campfire good-naturedly jollying and telling scary stories.
examples.ru: Они проводили ночи у костра, добродушно веселясь и рассказывая страшные истории.
